<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>٢٤٥٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> عِيَاض.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> معقل بن يسَار.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
